    <question number="2">
        <prompt>What role did technology play in exploration?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">It was not important</option>
            <option letter="b">It enabled long-distance navigation</option>
            <option letter="c">It prevented exploration</option>
            <option letter="d">It was used only for warfare</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>Technological advances in navigation, shipbuilding, and map-making made long-distance exploration possible.</explanation>
